org.nasdanika.html

Interface HTMLFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultHTMLFactory

    public interface HTMLFactory
    Implementations of this class abstract HTML rendering code from rendering of low-level HTML primitives.
    Author:
    Pavel
